This package contains 1 FreeBASIC file:

1 Main Program (./):
GematriaFBC.bas

===============================================================================
| User guide                                                                  |
===============================================================================
#####################
#   Installation    #
#####################
Linux 32- and 64-bit and Windows (32-bit) binaries are included in the Git
repository.

To compile on Linux:
fbc ./GematriaFBC.bas

To compile on Windows:
fbc GematriaFBC.bas

(Binaries compiled with FBG version 1.02.1)

#########################
#  General Information  #
#########################
Enter a phrase to find the gematria.  Enter !q to quit.
Gives Simple English, Regular English, Pythagorian and Reduced.  No Chaledean
(yet).
===============================================================================
